svg.title: FIGURE 16 MULTIPAIR NID OR BET TERMINAL CONNECTIONS CONTAINING FUSELESS STATION PROTECTORS

text.tspan: MULTIPAIR NID OR BET TERMINAL CONNECTIONS
#18 AWG coppercovered steel reinforced aeriol service conductors shall not be
connected to quick connect terminals. Nonmetallic reinforced aerial service
conductors (#22 AWG copper) may be connected to quick connect terminals.
